                    "body": "<p>Wouldn't it be easier to compute angle between vector to center of cone and vector from apex pointing at point under evaluation.  If vector projection is used and the length of the resultant vector is shorter then the vector pointing at the center of the cone the between the angle and length you know if you are inside a cone.</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vector_projection\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vector_projection</a></p>\n"
