            "title": "How can I detect if a point is inside a cone or not, in 3D space?",
            "body": "<p>How is possible to detect if a 3D point is inside a cone or not? </p>\n\n<pre><code>Ross cone = (x1, y1, h1)\nCone angle = alpha\nHeight of the cone = H\nCone radius = R\nCoordinates of the point of the cone = P1 (x2, y2, h2)\nCoordinates outside the cone = P2( x3, y3, h3)\n\nResult for point1 = true\nResult for point2 = false\n</code></pre>\n"
